                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; first words (headings or parts of headings) of constituent texts; directives for the ministers; name of the ruling king; some of the musical notation signs above the lines; abbreviations; elements of the punctuation signs and Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
